<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Spa Joliecao Beauty – Trợ Lý AI Đặt Lịch Tự Động</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --p:  #8b7355;
      --pd: #6b5640;
      --pl: #f5f0eb;
      --a:  #c9a96e;
      --bg: #faf9f7;
      --text: #2d2d2d;
    }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.95); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 14px 32px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    }
    .logo { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--p); }
    .logo span { color: var(--a); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--p); color: white; padding: 9px 20px;
      border-radius: 7px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      padding: 110px 20px 70px; text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fdfcfa 0%, #f5f0eb 60%, #ede5d8 100%);
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block; border: 1px solid var(--a); color: var(--p);
      padding: 5px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 50px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero h1 em { color: var(--p); font-style: normal; }
    .hero p { font-size: 16px; color: #666; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn {
      padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
    }
    .btn-solid  { background: var(--p); color: white; }
    .btn-outline { border: 2px solid var(--p); color: var(--p); background: white; }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features { padding: 72px 20px; background: white; }
    .sec-label { text-align: center; color: var(--a); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .sec-title { text-align: center; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 48px; }

    .feat-list { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .feat-item {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid #ede8e0; border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px 26px;
      transition: box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .feat-item:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(139,115,85,.1); }
    .feat-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; flex-shrink: 0;
      background: white; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; font-size: 26px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.07);
    }
    .feat-text h3 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .feat-text p  { font-size: 14px; color: #777; line-height: 1.65; }

    /* DEMO */
    .demo { padding: 72px 20px; background: var(--bg); }
    .demo-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .demo-title h2 { font-size: clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .demo-title p  { font-size: 14px; color: #777; }
    .demo-phones { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 36px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .demo-cta { text-align: center; }
    .demo-cta a { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; background: var(--p); color: white; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; }

    /* Phone shell */
    .phone { border-radius: 34px; padding: 9px; box-shadow: 0 20px 56px rgba(0,0,0,.22); margin: 0 auto; }
    .phone.dark-shell { background: #1c1c1e; }
    .phone.white-shell { background: #e8e8e8; box-shadow: 0 20px 56px rgba(0,0,0,.15), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .screen { border-radius: 26px; overflow: hidden; }

    /* ── ZALO ── */
    .zalo-bar {
      background: #0068ff; color: white;
      padding: 8px 12px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .zalo-status-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 9px; opacity: .9; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .zalo-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .zalo-back { font-size: 16px; opacity: .9; }
    .zalo-av {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: white;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .zalo-logo {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; background: #0068ff; border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: white; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 900; font-style: italic;
    }
    .zalo-info .zalo-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .zalo-info .zalo-sub  { font-size: 9px; opacity: .8; }
    .zalo-icons { margin-left: auto; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; opacity: .9; }
    .zalo-body { background: #f0f2f5; padding: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; min-height: 280px; }
    .zm { max-width: 82%; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.5; border-radius: 8px; }
    .zmb { background: white; color: #222; align-self: flex-start; border-radius: 2px 10px 10px 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .zmu { background: #d9f2ff; color: #003d99; align-self: flex-end; border-radius: 10px 2px 10px 10px; }
    .zmt { font-size: 9.5px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 2px; }
    .zbtns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; margin-top: 6px; }
    .zbtn { background: #e8f0ff; border: 1px solid #99bbff; color: #0052cc; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 500; }
    .zalo-inputbar { background: white; padding: 8px 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8; }
    .zinput { flex:1; background: #f0f2f5; border-radius: 18px; padding: 6px 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #999; }
    .zsend { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: #0068ff; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 12px; }

    /* ── WHATSAPP ── */
    .wa-statusbar { background: #075e54; color: white; padding: 5px 12px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 9px; }
    .wa-bar { background: #075e54; color: white; padding: 8px 12px 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .wa-av {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25d366; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .wa-logo { font-size: 18px; }
    .wa-info .wa-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
    .wa-info .wa-sub  { font-size: 9px; opacity: .8; }
    .wa-icons { margin-left: auto; display: flex; gap: 12px; font-size: 14px; opacity: .9; }
    .wa-body { background: #e5ddd5; background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23c8b89a' fill-opacity='0.15'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E"); padding: 10px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; min-height: 280px; }
    .wm { max-width: 82%; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.5; border-radius: 8px; position: relative; }
    .wmb { background: white; color: #222; align-self: flex-start; border-radius: 2px 8px 8px 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .wmu { background: #dcf8c6; color: #222; align-self: flex-end; border-radius: 8px 2px 8px 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .wmt { font-size: 9.5px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 2px; text-align: right; }
    .wbtns { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; margin-top: 6px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 6px; }
    .wbtn { color: #128c7e; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 2px 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
    .wa-inputbar { background: #f0f0f0; padding: 6px 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .wainput { flex:1; background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 7px 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #999; }
    .wasend { width: 30px; height: 30px; background: #075e54; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 13px; }

    /* PLANS */
    .plans-sec { padding: 72px 20px; background: white; }
    .plans { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 22px; align-items: start; }
    .plan { border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid #ede8e0; background: white; overflow: hidden; transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; }
    .plan:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .plan.featured { border-color: var(--p); transform: scale(1.03); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139,115,85,.18); }
    .plan.featured:hover { transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-5px); }
    .plan.pro { border-color: #6d28d9; }
    .plan-head { padding: 26px 24px 20px; }
    .plan-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .badge-b { background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; }
    .badge-a { background: var(--pl); color: var(--p); }
    .badge-p { background: #ede9fe; color: #6d28d9; }
    .plan-name { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .name-b { color: #64748b; } .name-a { color: var(--p); } .name-p { color: #6d28d9; }
    .plan-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #888; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .plan-price { font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; }
    .plan-price span { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #aaa; }
    .plan-note { font-size: 12px; color: #bbb; margin-top: 3px; }
    .plan-div { height: 1px; background: #f0ece6; margin: 0 24px; }
    .plan-feats { padding: 20px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    .pf { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 9px; font-size: 13px; color: #444; line-height: 1.45; }
    .pf-ic { flex-shrink: 0; width: 19px; height: 19px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 10px; margin-top: 1px; }
    .ic-b { background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; }
    .ic-a { background: var(--pl); color: var(--p); }
    .ic-p { background: #ede9fe; color: #6d28d9; }
    .pf small { display: block; font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 1px; }
    .new-tag { background: #fff7ed; color: #c2410c; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 6px; margin-left: 5px; }
    .plan-cta-wrap { padding: 0 24px 24px; }
    .plan-btn { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 12px; border-radius: 9px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-b { background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; }
    .btn-a { background: var(--p); color: white; }
    .btn-p { background: #6d28d9; color: white; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta {
      padding: 70px 20px; text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pd), var(--p), #a08060); color: white;
    }
    .cta h2 { font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 34px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cta p  { opacity: .85; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-w { background: white; color: var(--p); padding: 13px 26px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-o { border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6); color: white; padding: 13px 26px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; }

    footer { background: #2a2218; color: #777; padding: 26px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
    footer strong { color: var(--a); }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .plans { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .plan.featured { transform: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 12px 16px; }
      .demo-phones { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 300px; }
      .hero-btns .btn { width: 100%; max-width: 280px; justify-content: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">✦ <span>Joliecao</span> Beauty</div>
  <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Liên hệ ngay</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="tag">✨ Trợ lý AI đặt lịch spa</div>
  <h1>Khách đặt lịch 24/7<br><em>— bạn chỉ cần phục vụ</em></h1>
  <p>Tích hợp Zalo, không cần kỹ thuật, setup trong 1 ngày.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="#demo" class="btn btn-solid">💬 Xem bot demo</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Đăng ký miễn phí</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="sec-label">Tính năng</div>
  <div class="sec-title">Trợ lý AI làm gì cho spa của bạn?</div>

  <div class="feat-list">
    <div class="feat-item">
      <div class="feat-icon">💆</div>
      <div class="feat-text">
        <h3>Khách nhắn → chọn dịch vụ ngay</h3>
        <p>Khách mở Zalo nhắn tin, bot hiển thị ngay menu dịch vụ (massage, facial, nail…). Chọn xong là đặt — không cần gọi điện.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-item">
      <div class="feat-icon">📅</div>
      <div class="feat-text">
        <h3>Chọn ngày giờ → đặt lịch tự động</h3>
        <p>Khách chọn ngày và khung giờ phù hợp, bot kiểm tra lịch trống và xác nhận đặt hẹn ngay lập tức — hoàn toàn tự động.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-item">
      <div class="feat-icon">🔔</div>
      <div class="feat-text">
        <h3>Tự động nhắc lịch hẹn trước 1–2 tiếng</h3>
        <p>Trợ lý tự nhắn tin nhắc khách trước khi đến hẹn. Giảm tình trạng khách quên lịch, tăng doanh thu mỗi ngày.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-item">
      <div class="feat-icon">📋</div>
      <div class="feat-text">
        <h3>Xem lịch sử dịch vụ đã dùng</h3>
        <p>Khách tra cứu lại các lần sử dụng dịch vụ ngay trong chat. Spa biết sở thích từng khách để tư vấn đúng hơn.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-item">
      <div class="feat-icon">🎁</div>
      <div class="feat-text">
        <h3>Gửi khuyến mãi cho khách quen</h3>
        <p>Tự động gửi ưu đãi, voucher cho khách thân thiết vào dịp sinh nhật, lễ tết hoặc khi có chương trình mới của spa.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DEMO -->
<section class="demo" id="demo">
  <div class="sec-label">Demo</div>
  <div class="demo-title">
    <h2>Hoạt động trên Zalo & WhatsApp</h2>
